        "rich_text_D9zwK4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We have officially opened our doors to our first experience store in Chembur, Mumbai. We designed the store not to be merely a showroom, but to provide a luxurious experience to every visitor. Located in the heart of Chembur, this jewellery shop has been designed with as much thought as we put into our extraordinary jewelry designs. This diamond jewellery shop near me brings us closer to our growing community in Mumbai. For anyone looking for affordable luxury in Mumbai, Lucira Jewelry’s diamond shop now stands as a definite destination. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qFmX3i": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lucira Experience: The Home That Echoes Milestone Celebrations",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lucira Experience: The Home That Echoes Milestone Celebrations</h2>",
            "custom_id": "store"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_QCfPjA": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_cb146a69-b40c-411c-979d-bc20bc52bfe4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Each corner of the store tells a story. The soft lighting brings out the brilliance of every diamond, the textures of the interiors echo modern elegance, and the warmth of the staff makes it all feel deeply personal. From custom engagement rings to lab-grown diamond jewellery in Chembur, each creation celebrates Indian craftsmanship with a global aesthetic.</p><p>As the doors to our store opened, the murmur, the glint of diamonds, and the elegant, fresh flowers stood as symbols that, in a very short period of time, we delivered our promise of being extraordinary for our extraordinary clientele. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3UC84m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>As the ribbon was cut, it symbolized more than opening the store, but a new chapter in Lucira Jewelry’s story. The lighting of the Samay candle brought warmth and light into the space, reflecting Lucira’s philosophy of beginning every new chapter with gratitude and purpose. Vandana and Rupesh Jain, the founders of Lucira Jewelry delivered speeches about the vision of Lucira Jewelry and their gratitude towards all those who are part of this journey. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
